cher Alternativen und Veränderungspotenziale durch neue Formen kollektiver Interessenvertretung diskutiert.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aAltenbildung. 4aAltenpflege. 4aArbeit. 4aArbeits- und Industriesoziologie. 4aBerufsethos. 4aBildung. 4aEmotion. 4aGeschäftslogik. 4aPflege. 4aPolitik. 4aSolidarität. 4aSoziologie. 4aVorsorge. 4aWeiterbildung. 4aWirtschaftsethik. 4aWohlfahrtsstaat. 4aZivilgesellschaft. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aBusiness Ethics.  aBusiness Logic.  aCare.  aCivil Society.  aEducation.  aElderly Care.  aEmotion.  aFurther Education.  aOld Age Education.  aPolitics.  aProfessional Ethics.  aSociology of Work and Industry.  aSociology.  aSolidarity.  aWelfare State.  aWork.1 aBode, Ingo, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aParschick, Sarina, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2023z9783111318806oZDB-23-DSL08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2023z9783111024950oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839467220?locatt=mode:legacyzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839467220zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839467220/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-DSLb2023  aZDB-23-GOA  aZDB-23-TGPb2023